about the Paranormal Club?

335
00:24:15,668 --> 00:24:17,711
Don’t you want the Q.E.D. Club?

336
00:24:17,712 --> 00:24:19,629
- Huh?
- That’s an adventure, too.

337
00:24:19,630 --> 00:24:22,133
