Lori.

544
00:36:15,554 --> 00:36:16,762
Lori.

545
00:36:16,763 --> 00:36:19,308
Lori. Help me, Lori.

546
00:36:19,850 --> 00:36:20,850
Lori.

547
00:36:21,499 --> 00:36:24,294
You wanted to scare me,
so you did that, right?

548
00:36:31,570 --> 00:36:33,780
When you hid that tape recorder
under my bed

549
00:36:34,281 --> 00:36:36,782
you didn’t expect for me
to find a strand of your hair.

550
00:36:36,783 --> 00:36:37,783
Did you?

551
00:36:43,832 --> 00:36:45,751
Now that I think about it...

552
00:36:46,960 --> 00:36:50,380
your previous roommates
experienced the exact same thing.

553
00:36:51,423 --> 00:36:52,423
So…

554
00:36:52,674 --> 00:36:55,614
is it possible that you played
the same prank on them

555
00:36:55,928 --> 00:36:57,512
to make them move out

556
00:36:57,638 --> 00:37:00,057
so you could have this whole unit
to yourself?

557
00:37:00,682 --> 00:37:01,682
What?

558
00:37:02,017 --> 00:37:03,185
Am I right?

559
00:37:14,071 --> 00:37:15,071
Bravo!

560
00:37:16,782 --> 00:37:19,075
I did not expect you to figure it out

561
00:37:19,076 --> 00:37:20,452
in a matter of hours.

562
00:37:21,995 --> 00:37:23,330
And just to be clear,

563
00:37:24,039 --> 00:37:25,499
it was my intention

564
00:37:25,874 --> 00:37:27,751
to leave a strand of hair in your room.

565
00:37:29,461 --> 00:37:31,922
I want to know
if you’ll be able to notice it

566
00:37:32,339 --> 00:37:34,633
so you can connect it
to the tape recording.

567
00:37:38,762 --> 00:37:39,846
And...

568
00:37:40,430 --> 00:37:42,182
you failed to disappoint me.

569
00:37:44,518 --> 00:37:45,978
Think of it as a test.

570
00:37:46,812 --> 00:37:48,355
- Test?
- Yeah.

571
00:37:48,730 --> 00:37:50,190
To scare me?

572
00:37:50,691 --> 00:37:53,193
So you can force me out of this unit?

573
00:37:54,903 --> 00:37:56,238
Part of it, yes.

574
00:37:57,906 --> 00:37:59,323
I want to know

575
00:37:59,324 --> 00:38:02,244
if you deserve to stay in this unit.

576
00:38:02,245 --> 00:38:13,136
(Watch on www.kisskh.club Support Admin)

577
00:38:03,161 --> 00:38:04,161
And...

578
00:38:04,997 --> 00:38:06,289
I want to know...

579
00:38:07,416 --> 00:38:09,167
if my hunch about you is correct.

580
00:38:09,501 --> 00:38:10,711
What hunch?

581
00:38:11,378 --> 00:38:12,462
That you

582
00:38:13,088 --> 00:38:16,842
have above average observation skills.

583
00:38:19,094 --> 00:38:20,762
While I was reading your blog,

584
00:38:21,179 --> 00:38:25,480
I noticed how detailed you were
in describing every moment.

585
00:38:26,268 --> 00:38:28,186
You never let anything slide.

586
00:38:28,770 --> 00:38:30,439
I find that very impressive.

587
00:38:30,897 --> 00:38:31,982
So why?

588
00:38:32,274 --> 00:38:34,234
What do you need to confirm?

589
00:38:35,777 --> 00:38:37,362
That you deserve...

590
00:38:38,280 --> 00:38:39,531
to join my club.

591
00:38:40,824 --> 00:38:42,451
The result of my test on you

592
00:38:42,951 --> 00:38:44,578
made me want to recruit you more.

593
00:38:45,377 --> 00:38:46,837
Recruit my foot!

594
00:38:50,300 --> 00:38:51,333
Oh!

595
00:38:53,045 --> 00:38:54,755
So you’re rejecting my offer?

596
00:38:55,589 --> 00:38:57,506
Is that why you’ve been avoiding me
since yesterday

597
00:38:57,507 --> 00:38:59,543
at school and even here in the apartment?

598
00:39:00,177 --> 00:39:02,888
Excuse me, I'm not avoiding you!

599
00:39:04,514 --> 00:39:05,515
Are you sure?

600
00:39:07,059 --> 00:39:09,144
Based on the actions you’ve shown...

601
00:39:10,228 --> 00:39:13,398
you are showing an Avoidance Behavior.

602
00:39:13,899 --> 00:39:15,817
What are you even saying?

603
00:39:16,193 --> 00:39:17,778
It’s a form of defense mechanism

604
00:39:18,195 --> 00:39:20,780
where a person avoids certain situations

605
00:39:20,781 --> 00:39:24,534
that cause stress, fear,
and uneasy emotions.

606
00:39:27,204 --> 00:39:30,457
Oh, my God, can you please stop
psycho-analyzing my actions?

607
00:39:30,999 --> 00:39:34,502
Also, can you ask me
for a different favor instead?

608
00:39:34,503 --> 00:39:36,213
Let’s not talk about me joining the club.

609
00:39:37,130 --> 00:39:39,216
If you keep insisting on what you want

610
00:39:39,812 --> 00:39:42,273
sorry, but I can’t give it to you.

611
00:39:45,013 --> 00:39:46,055
Did you hear me?

612
00:39:46,056 --> 00:39:47,307
I said no!

613
00:39:48,266 --> 00:39:49,518
Yeah, I heard you.

614
00:39:51,228 --> 00:39:53,105
But you’re leaving me
with no other choice.

615
00:39:53,522 --> 00:39:54,731
What do you mean?

616
00:39:58,527 --> 00:39:59,486
How dare you!

617
00:39:59,487 --> 00:40:00,611
Delete that!

618
00:40:00,612 --> 00:40:01,947
How did you get that?

619
00:40:02,072 --> 00:40:04,699
You went into my room
without my permission?

620
00:40:05,033 --> 00:40:07,077
You should have installed more locks
on your door.

621
00:40:11,665 --> 00:40:12,833
Look at your photo.

622
00:40:13,333 --> 00:40:16,169
You probably won’t like it
if this spreads on social media.

623
00:40:16,586 --> 00:40:18,338
Are you blackmailing me?

624
00:40:18,463 --> 00:40:19,463
Am I?

625
00:40:20,257 --> 00:40:22,217
It doesn’t matter to me
as long it does the trick.

626
00:40:22,759 --> 00:40:24,969
Loki, I'm telling you!

627
00:40:24,970 --> 00:40:26,221
I dare you!

628
00:40:26,596 --> 00:40:28,180
I dare you.

629
00:40:28,181 --> 00:40:29,181
Loki!

630
00:40:30,350 --> 00:40:32,101
That’s a threat, you know.

631
00:40:32,102 --> 00:40:34,062
But you know what, go ahead.

632
00:40:34,271 --> 00:40:35,480
Post it.

633
00:40:35,939 --> 00:40:37,274
I don’t care.

634
00:40:37,941 --> 00:40:39,192
I’m not threatening you.

635
00:40:40,110 --> 00:40:41,670
I’m just reminding you of your promise.

636
00:40:43,071 --> 00:40:44,864
You said that you’re willing to help Lara.

637
00:40:44,865 --> 00:40:45,866
Lisa!

638
00:40:46,116 --> 00:40:47,158
Whatever.

639
00:40:47,159 --> 00:40:48,743
But whoever that student is...

640
00:40:49,035 --> 00:40:50,829
you told me to help her.

641
00:40:50,996 --> 00:40:52,414
Because you feel guilty

642
00:40:52,664 --> 00:40:53,999
when you don’t help her.

643
00:40:54,749 --> 00:40:56,459
You felt somewhat responsible.

644
00:40:57,294 --> 00:40:59,838
Now, all I’m asking for is what you said.

645
00:41:01,576 --> 00:41:02,619
Are you really like that?

646
00:41:03,466 --> 00:41:04,743
You can’t keep your word?

647
00:41:19,900 --> 00:41:21,193
Are you really like that?

648
00:41:21,902 --> 00:41:23,695
You can’t keep your word, Lorelei?

649
00:41:29,701 --> 00:41:32,704
Loki’s like my ghost,
he never leaves me alone.

650
00:41:33,413 --> 00:41:35,040
I may not like his attitude,

651
00:41:35,749 --> 00:41:37,751
but everything he says is true.

652
00:41:38,877 --> 00:41:40,128
Which really scares me.

653
00:41:40,879 --> 00:41:41,879
A lot.

654
00:41:43,089 --> 00:41:46,218
I admit it, I’m afraid of being judged.

655
00:41:46,885 --> 00:41:48,845
I’m scared my life will get messed up.

656
00:41:49,471 --> 00:41:51,723
I’m scared the truth will hit me hard.

657
00:41:53,052 --> 00:41:54,804
But despite all these fears,

658
00:41:55,227 --> 00:41:56,895
there is one thing true.

659
00:41:57,479 --> 00:41:58,855
I want to help others.

660
00:41:59,439 --> 00:42:01,650
I may not able to face my own fears,

661
00:42:02,234 --> 00:42:04,861
but perhaps I can help others face theirs.

662
00:42:13,703 --> 00:42:18,249
Focus on your studies
and stay out of trouble at school.

663
00:42:18,250 --> 00:42:20,450
Focus on your studies
and stay out of trouble at school.

664
00:42:26,800 --> 00:42:27,800
Okay.

665
00:42:30,637 --> 00:42:31,972
Just do it, Lori.

666
00:42:32,847 --> 00:42:33,847
Okay.

667
00:42:39,020 --> 00:42:40,020
Loki?

668
00:42:43,942 --> 00:42:45,235
Loki, are you there?

669
00:43:39,831 --> 00:43:41,081
To: Rhea
Subject: Just checking on you.

670
00:43:41,082 --> 00:43:42,250
Message: How are you doing?

671
00:43:42,275 --> 00:43:44,903
It's been three weeks
since I sent my last email to you.

672
00:43:45,128 --> 00:43:47,088
And you still haven't gotten back to me.

673
00:43:47,297 --> 00:43:49,340
Either you've been too busy to check

674
00:43:49,341 --> 00:43:52,218
or you don't open your e-mail
as regularly as I do.

675
00:43:53,386 --> 00:43:54,471
In any case,

676
00:43:54,763 --> 00:43:57,515
I'm writing to express
how the status quo bores me.

677
00:43:57,974 --> 00:43:59,141
Without you,

678
00:43:59,142 --> 00:44:02,270
this world lacks the colors it once had
when you were around.

679
00:44:02,854 --> 00:44:04,981
It has become dull and monotonous.

680
00:44:05,565 --> 00:44:07,984
I wonder how long
I can endure the mundane.

681
00:44:11,488 --> 00:44:13,073
Of all the people who know me,

682
00:44:13,698 --> 00:44:14,865
you are the most aware

683
00:44:14,866 --> 00:44:18,286
of how much I abhor
the dismal routine of existence.

684
00:44:19,454 --> 00:44:21,414
Everything is so ordinary.

685
00:44:22,123 --> 00:44:23,666
Everyone is so boring.

686
00:44:24,501 --> 00:44:26,002
And everything is so grey.

687
00:44:26,711 --> 00:44:29,589
I’ve been searching
for an added tinge of color in my life.

688
00:44:30,340 --> 00:44:33,593
But it has always escaped my grasp
ever since you left.

689
00:44:34,511 --> 00:44:35,594
You would surely agree with me

690
00:44:35,595 --> 00:44:38,098
when I say
that I need to find a distraction.

691
00:44:39,140 --> 00:44:42,310
An escape from this repetitive
and depressing reality.

692
00:44:43,103 --> 00:44:44,646
If you were only here,

693
00:44:45,438 --> 00:44:47,524
it would still be a lot of fun
and challenging.

694
00:44:49,484 --> 00:44:53,154
I always found your opposition
to my views thought-provoking.

695
00:44:54,322 --> 00:44:55,322
Now...

696
00:44:55,824 --> 00:44:57,783
I’m in a constant pursuit of diversion

697
00:44:57,784 --> 00:45:00,870
to keep my mind stimulated
and my monsters at bay.

698
00:45:02,163 --> 00:45:03,873
It may be an endless chase...

699
00:45:04,666 --> 00:45:07,001
and I don’t know
if it’s a worthwhile quest, but...

700
00:45:07,919 --> 00:45:10,505
this is the best alternative
I have so far.

701
00:45:11,714 --> 00:45:13,716
I look forward to hearing your stories.

702
00:45:15,427 --> 00:45:17,429
Please get back to me as soon as you can.

703
00:45:19,389 --> 00:45:20,389
Regards,

704
00:45:21,599 --> 00:45:22,434
Loki.

705
00:45:22,775 --> 00:45:24,527
Your curiosity would have you killed!

706
00:45:25,228 --> 00:45:26,229
Do you know that?

707
00:45:27,397 --> 00:45:29,732
Why did you just suddenly show up?

708
00:45:33,111 --> 00:45:37,740
I don’t remember giving you permission
to read my personal messages.

709
00:45:40,034 --> 00:45:42,162
That's a clear invasion of privacy!

710
00:45:44,456 --> 00:45:45,540
Yeah, right!

711
00:45:46,040 --> 00:45:48,292
Coming from someone
who was peeking at my messages

712
00:45:48,293 --> 00:45:49,627
while I was reading them.

713
00:45:49,752 --> 00:45:51,632
And someone
who comes into my room late at night

714
00:45:51,796 --> 00:45:54,548
to take pictures of me
while I was sleeping

715
00:45:54,549 --> 00:45:56,134
without my consent.

716
00:46:03,600 --> 00:46:05,768
You’re probably here
to join the Q.E.D. Club.

717
00:46:09,105 --> 00:46:10,105
Here’s the form.

718
00:46:10,982 --> 00:46:11,982
Fill it out.

719
00:46:48,895 --> 00:46:49,895
Are we good?

720
00:46:51,731 --> 00:46:53,233
Okay, quick orientation.

721
00:46:53,608 --> 00:46:56,110
The Q.E.D. Club

722
00:46:56,611 --> 00:47:00,114
is the one and only detective club
in Clark University.

723
00:47:00,490 --> 00:47:02,170
Its name is derived from the Latin phrase,

724
00:47:02,659 --> 00:47:06,621
Quod Erat Demonstrandum.

725
00:47:07,288 --> 00:47:08,706
Which means in English,

726
00:47:08,915 --> 00:47:10,959
“Which was to be demonstrated."

727
00:47:11,626 --> 00:47:14,546
That’s usually placed
at the end of math proofs

728
00:47:14,879 --> 00:47:16,672
or philosophical arguments

729
00:47:16,673 --> 00:47:20,009
to show that you’ve proven
what you set out to prove.

730
00:47:22,136 --> 00:47:23,513
Okay.

731
00:47:23,972 --> 00:47:25,482
Thanks for the info.

732
00:47:26,182 --> 00:47:28,476
So, what should I do?

733
00:47:29,269 --> 00:47:30,269
Well...

734
00:47:31,271 --> 00:47:34,148
our mission
is to investigate hidden truths...

735
00:47:35,567 --> 00:47:38,152
solve mysteries through logic and teamwork

736
00:47:38,444 --> 00:47:41,573
and protect the innocent
from deception and injustice.

737
00:47:42,240 --> 00:47:43,240
Noted.

738
00:47:43,908 --> 00:47:45,910
For your role, it’s pretty simple.

739
00:47:46,911 --> 00:47:49,789
You will help me collate requests
from clients.

740
00:47:49,914 --> 00:47:52,457
Once we’re in the investigation proper,

741
00:47:52,458 --> 00:47:54,877
I expect you to provide insights.

742
00:47:59,299 --> 00:48:02,135
I need you to observe more
in the case details,

743
00:48:02,343 --> 00:48:03,677
crime scenes,

744
00:48:03,678 --> 00:48:06,973
the people involved,
their stories and et cetera.

745
00:48:07,765 --> 00:48:08,765
And of course...

746
00:48:08,808 --> 00:48:11,227
don’t forget to take down notes
so we won’t miss anything.

747
00:48:12,353 --> 00:48:13,288
So...

748
00:48:13,313 --> 00:48:14,731
once we solve the case…

749
00:48:15,023 --> 00:48:17,483
your main task is to write about it

750
00:48:17,859 --> 00:48:19,444
and post it on your blog.

751
00:48:19,902 --> 00:48:20,902
Wait.

752
00:48:21,529 --> 00:48:22,988
So are you saying…

753
00:48:22,989 --> 00:48:25,617
you want me to be the club chronicler?

754
00:48:26,659 --> 00:48:27,744
Something like that.

755
00:48:28,870 --> 00:48:30,079
As you may notice

756
00:48:31,581 --> 00:48:33,583
the Q.E.D. Club isn’t popular yet

757
00:48:34,042 --> 00:48:35,460
among the students,

758
00:48:35,710 --> 00:48:38,087
freshmen and transferees.

759
00:48:39,297 --> 00:48:41,257
We can use your writing skills

760
00:48:41,591 --> 00:48:43,718
to advertise our club.

761
00:48:44,510 --> 00:48:45,803
Boost our popularity

762
00:48:46,262 --> 00:48:48,306
and attract more clients.

763
00:48:50,683 --> 00:48:52,352
So as Vice President,

764
00:48:52,894 --> 00:48:56,481
you are in charge
of media and public relations.

765
00:48:57,649 --> 00:48:58,649
Wait.

766
00:48:58,983 --> 00:49:01,152
I’m the club Vice President?

767
00:49:01,736 --> 00:49:03,821
I didn’t sign up for this.

768
00:49:05,239 --> 00:49:07,116
I’m the President of this club.

769
00:49:07,785 --> 00:49:09,370
So as a second member,

770
00:49:09,744 --> 00:49:10,828
by default,

771
00:49:11,287 --> 00:49:13,056
you’re the Vice President now.

772
00:49:15,009 --> 00:49:17,418
For now, we will wait for a client

773
00:49:17,460 --> 00:49:19,170
to come and tell us their story.

774
00:49:20,171 --> 00:49:22,757
Or if you don’t have
the patience to wait...

775
00:49:24,217 --> 00:49:25,343
you can leave.

776
00:49:26,177 --> 00:49:27,891
I’ll message you when we have a case.

777
00:49:28,596 --> 00:49:31,140
Your contact number
is in the form anyway.

778
00:49:34,894 --> 00:49:36,396
So, that's it?

779
00:49:37,667 --> 00:49:39,794
You actually joined the Q.E.D. Club?

780
00:49:41,593 --> 00:49:43,095
I’m really sorry, Rosetta.

781
00:49:43,403 --> 00:49:46,030
I’m just not really
into paranormal things.

782
00:49:46,572 --> 00:49:47,699
Too bad.

783
00:49:48,700 --> 00:49:51,284
But if you change your mind,
let me know, okay?

784
00:49:51,285 --> 00:49:52,870
It’s fun there. I promise.

785
00:49:53,204 --> 00:49:54,204
Alright.

786
00:49:54,414 --> 00:49:55,414
Thank you, though.

787
00:49:56,040 --> 00:49:57,040
No problem.

788
00:49:57,458 --> 00:49:58,500
But, wait.

789
00:49:58,501 --> 00:50:02,171
Are you still going to continue
your ghost hunting at Henson Apartment?

790
00:50:02,505 --> 00:50:04,589
I’m telling you,
there are no ghosts there.

791
00:50:04,590 --> 00:50:06,230
You’ll probably just end up disappointed.

792
00:50:06,676 --> 00:50:09,262
Exactly. We’ll just look
for somewhere else.

793
00:50:11,806 --> 00:50:13,808
Oh, no! Our class is about to start!

794
00:50:14,392 --> 00:50:15,392
Huh?

795
00:50:15,643 --> 00:50:16,619
Let’s go!

796
00:50:16,644 --> 00:50:18,562
Why didn’t the lunch bell ring?

797
00:50:18,563 --> 00:50:20,148
Did you hear it?

798
00:50:20,440 --> 00:50:21,416
I didn’t either.

799
00:50:21,441 --> 00:50:22,441
Maybe it's broken?

800
00:50:25,903 --> 00:50:26,903
Come on.

801
00:50:26,946 --> 00:50:27,946
Let’s go.

802
00:50:30,074 --> 00:50:33,077
Hurry! Hurry! Let's go.

803
00:50:33,327 --> 00:50:36,329
Come on, we’re late for the next class.
Ma’am is already there.

804
00:50:36,354 --> 00:50:39,357
Oh, no. What's that? What's happening?

805
00:50:39,382 --> 00:50:41,300
- It's so crowded.
- What happened?

806
00:50:42,587 --> 00:50:43,963
Why is everyone freaking out?

807
00:50:45,339 --> 00:50:46,215
Excuse me.

808
00:50:46,215 --> 00:50:47,008
Excuse me.

809
00:50:47,008 --> 00:50:48,008
Excuse me.

810
00:50:51,053 --> 00:50:52,430
Come on, let's check it out.

811
00:50:52,680 --> 00:50:53,806
We’re going to be late.

812
00:50:54,056 --> 00:50:55,141
Just for a second.

813
00:51:10,448 --> 00:51:11,824
Get them out of here!

814
00:51:13,910 --> 00:51:15,578
Go back to your classrooms!

815
00:51:16,204 --> 00:51:18,498
Go back! Go back! Go back.

816
00:51:19,540 --> 00:51:21,167
- Go back to your classroom.
- Go ahead.

817
00:51:23,795 --> 00:51:25,337
Go back to your classroom.

818
00:51:25,338 --> 00:51:27,423
- Go. Come on.
- Go back, go back.

819
00:51:27,965 --> 00:51:28,965
Go back.

820
00:51:33,721 --> 00:51:36,390
Consider this
our first official case together.

821
00:51:36,415 --> 00:51:39,085
I'm Chief Gareth Estrada.

822
00:51:39,528 --> 00:51:40,737
Don’t just stand there.

823
00:51:40,895 --> 00:51:41,896
We got some work to do.

824
00:51:44,899 --> 00:51:46,108
Have you seen this, Chief?

825
00:51:46,484 --> 00:51:47,777
According here...

826
00:51:48,402 --> 00:51:53,485
Isaac texted three people
with the same message.

827
00:51:53,510 --> 00:51:57,704
I called you here
because your president was found dead.

828
00:52:02,158 --> 00:52:03,409
Does that mean...

829
00:52:03,709 --> 00:52:05,753
he was killed to silence him?

830
00:52:07,588 --> 00:52:10,299
Look, the post already
has a lot of reactions and comments!

831
00:52:14,220 --> 00:52:15,391
What happened to him?

832
00:52:15,721 --> 00:52:16,888
Why is he like that?

833
00:52:16,889 --> 00:52:18,057
Lorelei Rios?

834
00:52:19,684 --> 00:52:20,935
Be honest with me.

835
00:52:21,644 --> 00:52:23,396
Were you forced to join that club?
